{"questionId":"9521","questionHtml":"<p>Use the eigenvalue method to find the general solution to this system of equations.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>The characteristic equation is given by</p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left| {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {3 - \\lambda }&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;{3 - \\lambda }  \\end{array}} \\right| = 0 \\Rightarrow {\\lambda ^2} - 6\\lambda + 5 = 0 \\Rightarrow \\lambda = 1{\\text{ or 5}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>|</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>λ</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>λ</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>|</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>λ</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>5</mn>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;or 5</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\lambda = 1{\\text{ }}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  2&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;2  \\end{array}} \\right)\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   q  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  0 \\\\   0  \\end{array}} \\right){\\text{ gives an eigenvector of form }}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>q</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;gives an eigenvector of form&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\lambda = 5{\\text{ }}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  { - 2}&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;{ - 2}  \\end{array}} \\right)\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   q  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  0 \\\\   0  \\end{array}} \\right){\\text{ gives an eigenvector of form }}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>5</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>q</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;gives an eigenvector of form&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>General solution is&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  x \\\\   y  \\end{array}} \\right) = A{e^t}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right) + B{e^{5t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>y</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mi>t</mi>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>5</mn>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[10 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9521","referenceCode":"EXM.2.AHL.TZ0.1a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Use the eigenvalue method to find the general solution to this system of equations.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 10]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.17—Phase portrait"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}